Interactive mode
  # When installing Elixir, you will have three new executables: iex, elixir, and elixirc
    40 + 2                        # 42
    "hello" <> "world" # "hello world"
  # To exit iex you must press Ctrl + C twice.

Running scripts
  # to run Elixir scripts can be used.
    IO.puts ("Hello world from Elixir")
    # save it with any name plus the extension .exs, and to execute it use the command elixir file_name.exsexs